<L>__{interior rec room morning}
<A>__{the sound belongs to a regular old treadmill like you see in most gyms across the world. running on it: sam bell, mid thirties, thick beard, handsome, striking blue eyes. sam's face is flushed and glistening with sweat. he lunges for a towel draped over the treadmill's bar, dabs his face as he runs. we see outside the window: a gray, powdery landscape stretching beneath a black sky.}
